<section class="key-highlights-section">
  <div class="container mx-auto py-5 px-4">
    <h2>The Smarter, Safer, and Stronger Way to Handle Hot Fryer Oil</h2>
    <p>
      The Shortening Shuttle<sup>®</sup> delivers safer hot oil transport, faster waste oil disposal, and unmatched
      durability for commercial kitchens. Engineered for restaurants, food trucks, and high-volume operations, it
      reduces burn risks, boosts efficiency, and provides long-lasting performance you can rely on every day.
    </p>
    <div class="highlights">
      <div class="highlight drop-shadow-xl" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-once="true">
        <img
          src="{{ 'images/safe.png' | asset_url }}"
          height="auto"
          width="80"
          class="mx-auto"
        >
        <h3>Safer Hot Oil Transport for Commercial Kitchens</h3>
        <p class="highlight-description">
          Protect your team and your flooring. The Shortening Shuttle<sup>®</sup> keeps hot fryer oil fully contained,
          minimizing burns, spills, and slip hazards during transport. Designed for restaurants, food trucks, and
          high-volume kitchens, it turns one of the industry’s most dangerous tasks into a controlled, compliant,
          OSHA-friendly workflow.
        </p>
        <p>
          {{ 'Learn more about key concepts' | link_to: 'https://shopify.dev/docs/storefronts/themes/architecture' }}
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="highlight drop-shadow-xl" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" data-aos-once="true">
        <img
          src="{{ 'images/down.png' | asset_url }}"
          height="auto"
          width="80"
          class="mx-auto"
        >
        <h3>Reduce Labor & Streamline Fryer Oil Disposal</h3>
        <p class="highlight-description">
          Stop wasting time wrestling with buckets, carts, or makeshift tools. The Shortening Shuttle<sup>®</sup> makes
          cooking oil removal faster, cleaner, and more efficient—helping kitchens maintain uptime, speed service, and
          reduce staff fatigue. Ideal for any operation looking to simplify waste oil management and improve
          back-of-house productivity.
        </p>
        <p>{{ 'View the Liquid reference' | link_to: 'https://shopify.dev/docs/api/liquid' }}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="highlight drop-shadow-xl" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400" data-aos-once="true">
        <img
          src="{{ 'images/flag.png' | asset_url }}"
          height="auto"
          width="80"
          class="mx-auto"
        >
        <h3>American-Built Durability Built for Daily Use</h3>
        <p class="highlight-description">
          Invest in equipment that lasts. Proudly made in the USA, the Shortening Shuttle<sup>®</sup> features rugged
          aluminum construction engineered for demanding commercial environments. It withstands heat, heavy use, and
          constant movement—delivering long-term reliability, lower replacement costs, and unmatched return on
          investment.
        </p>
        <p>{{ 'Follow best practices' | link_to: 'https://shopify.dev/docs/storefronts/themes/best-practices' }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% stylesheet %}
  .key-highlights-section {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }
  .key-highlights-section .highlights {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .key-highlights-section .highlights {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .key-highlights-section .highlight {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background-color: #eef3ff;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .key-highlights-section .highlight > * + * {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .key-highlights-section .highlight h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .key-highlights-section .highlight-description {
    flex: 1 1;
  }

  .key-highlights-section .highlight a {
    display: flex;
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: #20204b;
    color: white;
    border: 1px solid #20204b;
    border-radius: 5px;
    padding: 3px 10px 5px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
{% endstylesheet %}
